name: Briana Morris
text: It was so amazing the kids loved it they got to hold some bearded dragons and feed the fish. Plus the lady that owns it is so so sweet

name: Bradley Johnson
text: Friendly helpful staff. Family owned and operated by people that know the hobby very well.  By far the biggest and best selection in the area, everything from goldfish and guppies to arowana. This fish keeper highly recommends this store to everyone from beginners to experts, there is somthing here for you!

name: Billy Lee
text: Very very nice people!!! They helped me pick out the Koi fish i wanted and was very eager to answer all my questions. Check them out!

name: Stephen Mathews
text: Knowledgeable, helpful and just a great family to do business with!

name: Amyrillas Roberts
text: These people are so nice and kind they help u right away with no hesitation. I bought several fish from them they are just so amazing at there job and the  fish are Absolutely amazing as well they have all types of small fish and also larger fish and other sizes they also sell things like tanks and stuff to go in it ...... I highly suggest you guys checking them out

name: Fresca Simmons
text: They are very polite and knowledgeable. Definitely better than the chain stores. The only place we shop now.

name: Emily Pyle
text: Highly recommend checking out this fish store! They helped us start up our first freshwater tank, gave us tons of helpful information about the tank and the fish. They really know their stuff and don’t just try to sell stuff to sell it, they are super genuine and very knowledgable. We’ve been to several different fish stores in the surrounding areas and this is by far the best! Huge selection of unique fish, aquarium supplies, tanks, plants and more!

name: Dan Public
text: Terrific  place to relax and learn about fish...very informative folks...Smiles and helpfulness...gotta check these guys out...we use it like a homeschool class...walk in , ask questions..they are friendly and knowledgeable...cant say enough about this family...and they have lots of critters to choose from. 👍🙏✌🇺🇸

name: Justin Warr
text: Awesome fish store!!!! Huge variety of fish, supplies and tanks! Very knowledgeable staff. I highly recommend this store.

name: Lisa Jones
text: I love this place and the owners

name: Jessica Smith
text: Always able to answer the many questions we have that go along with owning fish. If they don't have something they will price it out for is and get it ordered!

name: Carlee Dalton
text: Kind people go there everyday they have some cool fish and low prices

name: Pam Albrecht
text: Owner was very knowledgeable and helpful. Lots of variety. Great to have an alternative to going to a city and a chain store.

name: Brandon Garrett
text: A very nice family who are always helpful. A lot a fish to choose from and they make sure that the fish they sell are healthy.

name: Jeffrey Thompson
text: Great ownership and quality livestock.... I highly recommend!!!

name: Jeanette Blount
text: Very helpful .. lots of fish to choose from
